Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}解除 Poker Face
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:22.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}完全等身大の赤裸々Talkで
